<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10240>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Harperocallis robustior. A Habit B Leaf (detail of parallel veins and tomentose margins) C Inflorescence (detail showing peduncular and calycular bracts subtending flowers) D Peduncular bracts (detail) E Flower F Tepal (adaxial view) G Ovary (note the tuberculae) H Ovary (cross-section showing axile placentation and ovules) I Capsule (carpels separating distally). (A, I from L. J. Dorr et al. 4967 (US); B-H from B. Stergios et al. 17327 (PORT)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10240" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

